<h5 id="step-2-use-data-attribute-in-html-markup">Step 2. Use data attribute in HTML markup</h5>

<p>Apply <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">data</code> attribute tags to your HTML, where <em>n</em> is the available feature you want to set, for example:</p>

